{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["「魔女達」の前夜祭\n\n<size=45>その四　消えたカボチャ<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"すまん、今は緊急事態じゃ――吾輩の作った南瓜焼菓子を見たか？","actor":301171,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:19}","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"うちは見てへんのやけど……どないした？","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:87}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":306051},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"陽炎の焼いたパンプキンパイ、消えまひた……","actor":301180,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:20}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"全く恨めしいのじゃ！……妹たちに一番美味しい焼菓子を食べさせようと、吾輩は３週間も頑張ったのじゃぞ！まさか焼き上げたばかりに盗まれたとは……","actor":301171,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:19}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"パイが焼き上がった後、陽炎が着替えるために部屋に戻っていた間、妾はずっとここでぼーーーーっとしておりました。――そしていつの間に……","actor":301180,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:20}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"そうなのじゃ。吾輩が着替え終わった時には全部なくなっていたのじゃ――","actor":301171,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:19}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"全部ではございませんよ。一個だけ、妾がいただきました。美味しゅうございました（じゅるり","actor":301180,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:20}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"おおお本当じゃな！この姉にウソを言うのは禁止じゃぞ！","actor":301171,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:19}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"っちゅうことは、部屋にいたのは二人だけなんやな？","actor":306051,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:87}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"へへ、実は私もいた。","actor":102091,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":-1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"クリーブランドか！？","actor":306051,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:87}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"ヘレナが作ってくれたハロウィン衣装だ。「我はリーパー、魂を刈り取る悪魔なり」どう？へへ～","actor":102091,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":-1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"んで、あの時はちょうど陽炎級の部屋を通りかかったんだけど……陽炎が着替えていた間は誰も玄関から入ってこなかったよ。","actor":102091,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":-1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"「通りかかった」なのにずっとそこにいたのか…","actor":301171,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:19}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"時は金なり！…ってことだけど、まあ、私だって時には贅沢したくなるんだぜ。","actor":102091,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":-1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"じ――――","actor":301171,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:19}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"クリーブランドじゃないです。この格好でパイは隠せないのです。","actor":301051,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:6}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"say":"で、他に私にできることは？","actor":102091,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":-1,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"海の騎士と名乗るなら、他人の部屋をあまり「通りがかりすぎ」のではなくて……？","actor":301180,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:20}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ハロウィンの準備は十分でございます。姉ぇの分はなくとも……","actor":301180,"d